             was indicted for <rs id="t17990911-9-off43" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17990911-9-off43" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990911-9-off43" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17990911-9-cd44" type="crimeDate">19th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990911-9-off43 t17990911-9-cd44"></join>, four pounds of raw coffee, value 4s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17990911-9-victim101" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Knight
               <interp inst="t17990911-9-victim101" type="surname" value="Knight"></interp>
